properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 17 at 3:12AM CST until February 17 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Corpus Christi TX
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one mile or less.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Port Aransas to Matagorda Ship
Channel out 20 NM, Bays and Waterways from Baffin Bay to Port
Aransas, Coastal waters from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas out 20
NM and Bays and Waterways from Port Aransas to Port O'Connor.

* WHEN...Until noon CST today.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON CST TODAY
